author: JayzTwoCents
description:
TDP is something that is often misunderstood and it doesn't help that the TDP specs of most CPUs is sort of a lie... so today we talk about it and how to plan your PC cooling based on ACTUAL power draw and not what's written on the misleading spec sheets.
